I'm telling you, B.B.

11:02.383 --> 11:04.565
She's a fucking spook. -Do?

11:04.609 --> 11:07.337
Robert, please tell me
you have evidence.

11:07.381 --> 11:08.933
There were noises.

11:08.977 --> 11:11.305
I heard... I heard noises
in my apartment.

11:11.329 --> 11:14.351
And she took my mail and...
And she's always around,

11:14.395 --> 11:16.891
in the hallway, outside,
always running into me.

11:16.915 --> 11:19.937
And Basarov,
the day he fucking bled out,

11:19.981 --> 11:22.393
she stopped my watch.
She bent the pin.

11:22.417 --> 11:24.157
