right?

11:27.121 --> 11:29.177
You've been under
a lot of stress.

11:29.221 --> 11:32.747
No. No.
This isn't about Daniel.

11:32.791 --> 11:35.183
We're all grieving.

11:35.227 --> 11:38.039
But we're moving against Platov
and I need you.

11:38.083 --> 11:40.559
